text: Vaughanella is a genus of small corals in the family Caryophylliidae. ==Species== The World Register of Marine Species includes the following species in the genus : *Vaughanella concinna Gravier, 1915 *Vaughanella margaritata (Jourdan, 1895) *Vaughanella multipalifera Cairns, 1995 *Vaughanella oreophila Keller, 1981 ==References== Category:Caryophylliidae Category:Scleractinia genera
title: Vaughanella
